trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 또는 앞으로 탐색 기록에서 항목을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]이전에 탐색, 탐색 기록에서와 마찬가지로 콘텐츠의 각 부분에 대 한 하나의 항목을 저장 하는 탐색 기록 서비스 구현 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 탐색 기록에는 두 스택, 탐색 기록 기억 하 고 다른 하나는 앞으로 탐색 기록 기억 구성 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: 현재 항목에 대 한 항목이 후방 앞으로 탐색 발생할 때 탐색 기록에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: 다음과 같은 상황에서이 오류 발생:- `Navigate` 메서드는 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: - `GoForward` 메서드는 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -탐색 모음에서 전달 단추 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 현재 탐색기에서 표시 되는 ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 탐색이 발생 하기 전에 현재 항목에 대 한 항목이 앞으로 탐색 기록에 추가 되는 마찬가지로, 경우:- `GoBack` 메서드는 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -탐색 모음에 뒤로 단추 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 현재 탐색기에서 표시 되는 ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: 각 항목 뒤에 앞으로 탐색 기록은 JournalEntry 클래스의 인스턴스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: 항목에 대 한 이름을 포함 하 여 특정 탐색에 대 한 정보를 캡슐화 하는 각 JournalEntry 개체 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>) 항목은 활성 상태로 유지 여부에 관계 없이 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) 및 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] 탐색 되는 콘텐츠에 대 한 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: 열거 하 여 탐색 기록의 모든 JournalEntry 개체를 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>또는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: 앞으로 탐색 기록에 대 한 모든 JournalEntry 개체를 열거 하 여 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>또는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 탐색 기록에서 가장 최근의 JournalEntry 개체를 제거 해야 할 경우, 탐색을 방지 하기 위해 예를 들어, 호출할 수 있습니다는 `RemoveBackEntry` 메서드 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), JournalEntry 개체를 제거 합니다.에 대 한 참조를 반환 하는</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: 하지만 추가할 수 없습니다 JournalEntry 개체 탐색 기록 인스턴스화할 하거나 JournalEntry에서 파생 될 수 있습니다 하 고 이렇게 하려면 멤버를 구현 하는 형식이 있기 때문입니다.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 사용자 지정 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>개체를 호출 하 여 탐색 기록을 다시 추가할 수 있습니다는 `AddBackEntry` 메서드 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>추가 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>개체를 내부적으로 만든 JournalEntry 하는 개체를 뒤로 탐색 기록에 추가 됩니다.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>
